INSERT INTO `enquiry` VALUES (22,'Jason','dcosta','jason@tomahawk.co.nz','','Tomahawk Test','A','2017-02-14 21:39:51','114.23.241.67'),(23,'Natasha','Adams','natasha.adams@fbu.com','095718140','Hi there,\r\n\r\nDoes your charity trust need help during the below date and time?\r\n\r\nWe are running a senior leadership programme for Fletcher building. For their first workshop we are running an Amazing Race which includes various activities including volunteering their time to a community initiative (to see the impact it‚Äôs having on the community).\r\n\r\nI have been recommended to contact your organisation. \r\n\r\nWe don‚Äôt mind what they are doing. The ideal is for the group to see first-hand the impact that the initiative has had on the community but if it‚Äôs behind the scenes only, we can work with that. \r\n\r\nDate: Wednesday 26th July\r\nTime: Start anytime e.g 6 or 8am  ‚Äì finish by 10am.\r\nLocation: We are flexible as long as they can get back to the city by 10.30am\r\nNumber of people: Group of 10-12 (men and women of various ages)\r\nRequirements: It is great for the teams to speak to those who have knowledge of the charity to hear a bit about the background also. It‚Äôs ideal if they can during their time volunteering they can see the impact they have made on the community/charity e.g meeting those who receive the service if possible.\r\n\r\nKind regards,\r\nNatasha Adams','A','2017-07-04 05:18:43','202.36.8.53'),(24,'Keith','Denne','keith.denne@gmail.com','021 125 1929','St Paul\'s Church recently sent a donation of $5000.00 to the Auckland Rescue Helicopter Trust. A receipt was sent but the amount stated was for $500.00 NOT $5000.00. Receipt number: 12470/96535.\r\n\r\nIf you could amend the donation to the correct amount ($5000.00) we would be grateful ( as well as our Auditor)\r\n\r\nMany thanks\r\n\r\nKeith Denne (for St Paul\'s Church)','A','2017-07-06 09:01:58','118.90.126.110'),(25,'CaseyJerGC','CaseyJerGC','uikd@articlegym.com','uikd@articlegym.com','We are Amiga toy CPS affiliate program, our affiliate have feature of easy use, high commission, high conversion rate. We offer great conditions, Lifetime Rev share start at 30% up to 50% depend on sales. Paid on every package customer purchases. Weekly, biweekly, monthly payments based on sales volume. \r\nWe work with US and most Europe countries. We accept all kinds of traffic. search \"Amiga toy affiliate\" on google to reach us. link: http://aff.oc4pa.com','A','2017-07-07 11:06:09','209.134.5.6'),(26,'Caleb','Hadfield','camerachamp@gmail.com','','Hello, I was wondering, if I get paramedic certified in the United states and fly on a medic Heli, do I  have to get re-certified to work in New Zealand as a flight medic?','A','2017-07-09 02:04:51','24.254.172.185'),(27,'Michael','Northcott','cetacean@orcon.net.nz','0272247356','Are you still fundraising via the entertainment book as i have tried to find you when renewing so you get the commission. Not successfully so am awaiting your reply. Thank you.\r\nMichael','A','2017-07-09 07:23:45','121.98.178.171'),(28,'Maree','Walsh','wakefieldmaree@gmail.com','274053204','Hi\r\n\r\nI have moved and no longer wish to be on your mailing list. Please remove me.\r\n\r\nMy details as you have the are:\r\nM Walsh\r\n7 Merivale Avenue\r\nEpsom\r\nAuckland 1023\r\n\r\nkind regards\r\nMaree','A','2017-07-10 21:49:53','118.92.193.141'),(29,'Sean','li','sean@tomahawk.co.nz','333','ferfeferf','A','2018-01-22 20:47:49','114.23.241.67'),(30,'sean','li','123@qq.com','123','sdaz','A','2018-01-22 20:48:24','114.23.241.67'),(31,'fef','ewfwe','sean@tomahawk.co.nz','24234','fwefwefwf','A','2018-01-22 20:49:28','114.23.241.67'),(32,'sean','li','sean@tomahawk.co.nz','0123','test','D','2018-01-22 21:19:26','114.23.241.67'),(33,'Test','Test','alan@tomahawk.co.nz','1234','Testing Chrome Bequest','D','2018-01-23 01:38:14','114.23.241.67'),(34,'Test','Test','alan@tomahawk.co.nz','1234','Testing Firefox','D','2018-01-23 01:41:13','114.23.241