ons, if you have made a donation you need to withdraw or dispute please&nbsp;contact us. &nbsp; DELIVERY &amp; RECEIPTING Delivery costs are included in the purchase price of all merchandise A physical receipt will be issued within 7-10 days of merchandise being sent Regular giving donations will be issued at the end of each financial year, one off donations will be posted after payment has been processed CURRENCY All prices are in New Zealand dollars &nbsp; CANCELLATION If you wish to withdraw your ongoing support of our organisation, please&nbsp;contact us.','','<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Website Temporarily Shutdown</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Thank you for visiting the Auckland Rescue Helicopter Trust&#39;s website. We are currently shutdown as we deal with an internal emergency. We respectfully ask that you wait for official communications regarding this matter to be released in due course.</p>');
